title: BOB SOVEN'S EXECUTIVE DECISION
description:
Bob Soven is happy making a living doing what he loves and doesn't mind being all business, all the time. Here, Bob demonstrates the happy approach to the 9-to-5 lifestyle in the new Discord. 

Music by The Unknown Komic
